#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:76
msgid ""
"Tokens and API keys that carry the legacy scope names keep working: the "
"server transparently maps legacy names to their replacements. This "
"compatibility mapping is deprecated and will be removed in a future "
"release, so update any automation that grants permissions to use the new "
"names."
msgstr ""
"携带旧权限范围名称的令牌和 API Key 仍然可用：服务器会透明地将旧名称映射到"
"新名称。该兼容映射已被弃用，并将在未来版本中移除，因此请更新所有授予权限"
"的自动化脚本，改用新名称。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:82
msgid "New default web UI (Next.js)"
msgstr "新的默认 Web UI（Next.js）"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:84
msgid ""
"The web UI has been rewritten in Next.js and is now the default; the "
"legacy React UI has been removed. The UI is exported statically at build "
"time and served by the Xinference server itself — no separate frontend "
"process is needed."
msgstr ""
"Web UI 已使用 Next.js 重写并成为默认界面；旧版 React UI 已被移除。UI 在"
"构建时静态导出，并由 Xinference 服务器本身提供服务——无需单独的前端进程。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:89
msgid ""
"The ``XINFERENCE_FRONTEND_ENDPOINT`` environment variable has been "
"**removed**. To serve a custom frontend build, point "
"``XINFERENCE_FRONTEND_DIST_DIR`` at its directory instead."
msgstr ""
"``XINFERENCE_FRONTEND_ENDPOINT`` 环境变量已被 **移除**。若要提供自定义的"
"前端构建产物，请改用 ``XINFERENCE_FRONTEND_DIST_DIR`` 指向其所在目录。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:92
msgid ""
"The old ``/ui/`` path redirects to ``/``. Opening ``/`` takes you to the "
"model launch page."
msgstr "旧的 ``/ui/`` 路径会重定向到 ``/``。打开 ``/`` 即进入模型启动页面。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:96
msgid "Built-in Gradio demo pages are removed"
msgstr "内置 Gradio 演示页面已移除"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:98
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The per-model Gradio demo UI (previously mounted at ``/{model_uid}``) and"
" the ``/v1/ui/*`` endpoints behind it have been removed, along with the "
"``gradio`` dependency. To interact with a running model, use the web UI, "
"the OpenAI-compatible API, or the Python client instead."
msgstr ""
"针对每个模型的 Gradio 演示 UI（之前挂载在 ``/{model_uid}``）及其背后的 ``"
"/v1/ui/*`` 接口已被移除， ``gradio`` 依赖也一并移除。若要与运行中的模型"
"交互，请改用 Web UI、OpenAI 兼容 API 或 Python 客户端。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:104
msgid "Strict Qwen3-family system-message ordering"
msgstr "严格的 Qwen3 系列系统消息顺序"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:106
msgid ""
"For model families whose chat template requires the system message to "
"come first (including Ornith-1.0-35B, qwen3.5, qwen3.6, and Nex-N2), "
"Xinference now validates message order before dispatching a request. A "
"``system`` message at any position other than ``messages[0]`` returns "
"HTTP 400. Move all system instructions into a single leading system "
"message before upgrading."
msgstr "对于聊天模板要求系统消息位于首位的模型系列（包括 Ornith-1.0-35B、qwen3.5、qwen3.6 和 Nex-N2），Xinference 现在会在分发请求前验证消息顺序。若 ``system`` 消息不在 ``messages[0]``，将返回 HTTP 400。升级前，请将所有系统指令合并到一条位于首位的系统消息中。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:113
msgid "Docker Compose requirements"
msgstr "Docker Compose 版本要求"

#: ../../source/getting_started/migration_3_0.rst:115
msgid ""
"The bundled Compose files dropped the deprecated ``version:`` field and "
"use newer Compose features, so deploying with them requires **Docker "
"Compose v2.24.4 or later**. See :ref:`using_docker_compose`."
msgstr ""
"随附的 Compose 文件移除了已弃用的 ``version:`` 字段，并使用了较新的 "
"Compose 特性，因此使用它们部署需要 **Docker Compose v2.24.4 或更高版本**"
"。参见 :ref:`using_docker_compose`。"
